I felt greedy for saying "if I get enough requests" since its not that good of a release.

The original plan for this was to be by object name and object option text, but alot of objects are apparently null. So, I had to manually input open and closed gate IDs. You must align each ID accordingly (if you put the closed ID in the first section of the array, you add it's open ID in the first section of the other array).

